title: (Mon Early Bird) Allie Colleen Performs A New Song + Pick A Bit Returns! Mailbag: Friend’s Wedding or Carrie Underwood Concert
itunes:title: (Mon Early Bird) Allie Colleen Performs A New Song + Pick A Bit Returns! Mailbag: Friend’s Wedding or Carrie Underwood Concert
description:
New artist Allie Colleen stops by to talk about her tattoos, her new song Halos and Horns and her biggest fear she lives with on the internet. Bobby brings back Pick A Bit where we vote on what member’s segment we want to hear. A listener needs advice on whether to go see Carrie Underwood with a Meet and Greet opportunity or go to their friend’s wedding.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
